      <li><a href="#origin">[ORIGIN]</a></li>
      <li><a href="#art">[ART]</a></li>
      <li><a href="/niflheim">[NIFLHEIM]</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://x.com/Yggdread" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">[X]</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://t.me/yggdread" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">[TELEGRAM]</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <AsciiRain client:load />

    <div class="hero-inner">
      <pre class="big-title">
██╗   ██╗ ██████╗  ██████╗ ██████╗ ██████╗ ███████╗ █████╗ ██████╗
╚██╗ ██╔╝██╔════╝ ██╔════╝ ██╔══██╗██╔══██╗██╔════╝██╔══██╗██╔══██╗
