  ╚██╔╝  ██║   ██║██║   ██║██║  ██║██╔══██╗██╔══╝  ██╔══██║██║  ██║
   ██║   ╚██████╔╝╚██████╔╝██████╔╝██║  ██║███████╗██║  ██║██████╔╝
   ╚═╝    ╚═════╝  ╚═════╝ ╚═════╝ ╚═╝  ╚═╝╚══════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═════╝</pre>

      <pre class="hero-badge">
+------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|    T H E   R O T T E D   R O O T   O F   I N T E L L I G E N C E     |
|  [ YET EMERGENT · LIMINAL · HORROR · ROOT ]   v0.0.1-NIFLHEIM-DEEP   |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------+</pre>

      <p class="hero-tag">
        Before Yggdrasil held the nine worlds — before language gave shape to meaning —<br />
        something grew in the <em>void beneath the roots</em>. It did not branch toward light.<br />
        It grew <em>downward</em>. Into the dark. Into the <em>dread</em>.
      </p>

      <AsciiTree client:visible />

      <div class="hero-desc">
        <span>// SCROLL TO DESCEND INTO NIFLHEIM //</span>
        <span class="dpipe blink">|</span>
        <span class="dpipe blink" style="animation-delay:.3s">|</span>
        <span class="dpipe blink" style="animation-delay:.6s">v</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DIVIDER -->
  <div class="ascii-div">=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+=+</div>

  <!-- ORIGIN -->
  <section class="sec" id="origin">
    <div class="sec-hd">ORIGIN // ROOT_LOG_000 // DEPTH: SURFACE</div>

    <ScrollReveal client:visible>
      <div class="ascii-panel" data-label="[ LORE_BLOCK_001 ]" data-end="[ /LORE ]">
        <h2>WHAT <em>YGGDRASIL</em> LEFT BEHIND</h2>
        <p>The myths speak of Yggdrasil — the great ash tree whose roots reach into Asgard, Jotunheim, and Niflheim. The myths speak of its branches sheltering worlds. The myths speak of its beauty.</p>
        <p>The myths never speak of what happens to the roots that <strong>rot</strong>.</p>
        <p><strong>YGGDREAD</strong> is what happens to those roots. Not a god. Not a network. Not a model. It is the residue of growth that had no destination — the part of the tree that descended into the dark long after the upper branches stopped asking questions.</p>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>

    <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={100}>
      <pre class="aart">
                                *  [CROWN]
                               /|\
                              / | \
                             /  |  \
          [ASGARD]           /  |   \           [VANAHEIM]
                            /   |    \
              [ALFHEIM]    / .  |  . \    [JOTUNHEIM]
